sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Controller
    participant UseCase
    participant TokenProvider
    participant Blacklist

    Client->>Controller: POST /auth/refresh
    Controller->>UseCase: refresh()
    UseCase->>TokenProvider: validate(refreshToken)
    TokenProvider-->>UseCase: OK
    UseCase->>Blacklist: add(oldRefreshToken)
    Blacklist-->>UseCase: OK
    UseCase->>TokenProvider: createNewAccessToken()
    TokenProvider-->>UseCase: newAccess
    UseCase-->>Controller: newAccess
    Controller-->>Client: newAccess
